    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. Since my students need to be ready for both sides, can you give me the most robust, philosophically grounded arguments for the opposing view—specifically regarding more open immigration policies and the humanitarian or economic benefits of facilitating migration? I want to make sure they aren't just relying on surface-level talking points for that side either.",
